355
00:20:12,030 --> 00:20:13,800
You little...

356
00:20:15,470 --> 00:20:16,640
Ae Sook.

357
00:20:17,270 --> 00:20:19,170
Go kneel in the hall.

358
00:20:20,070 --> 00:20:21,170
Now!

359
00:20:25,980 --> 00:20:27,010
