555
00:30:36,290 --> 00:30:37,390
You brat.

556
00:30:38,120 --> 00:30:40,460
After all we did to raise you...

557
00:30:40,590 --> 00:30:42,130
What did you...

558
00:30:42,360 --> 00:30:44,730
