- Stop it!

563
00:30:53,770 --> 00:30:56,340
- Move.
- Stop it.

564
00:30:56,340 --> 00:30:59,180
- Move!
- Please stop, sir.

565
00:30:59,750 --> 00:31:01,550
Don't hit Jung Hee!

566
00:31:05,420 --> 00:31:06,720
Move.

567
00:31:06,990 --> 00:31:08,220
Hello?

568
00:31:09,120 --> 00:31:11,120
Is anyone in?

569
00:31:11,760 --> 00:31:12,830
Someone's here.

570
00:31:16,330 --> 00:31:17,400
Someone's here?

571
00:31:18,060 --> 00:31:19,160
Someone's here.

572
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:24,870
Someone's here. Clean up.

573
00:31:25,770 --> 00:31:26,770
Who is it?

574
00:31:33,850 --> 00:31:35,310
Ma'am.

575
00:31:35,580 --> 00:31:38,150
I agree with everything you said...

576
00:31:38,150 --> 00:31:40,190
at the school today.

577
00:31:40,190 --> 00:31:43,490
If I could have my way,
I'd like to kick out...

578
00:31:43,790 --> 00:31:45,690
this wretched wench.

579
00:31:45,690 --> 00:31:47,090
Ma'am.

580
00:31:48,060 --> 00:31:50,430
Can't you forgive her just this once?

581
00:31:50,860 --> 00:31:52,830
Ae Sook should be punished...

582
00:31:52,830 --> 00:31:54,770
for what she did.

583
00:31:55,130 --> 00:31:57,170
But she's still a child.

584
00:31:57,170 --> 00:31:58,940
As a fellow mother...

585
00:31:58,940 --> 00:32:00,910
We understand what you mean.

586
00:32:03,140 --> 00:32:06,650
I knew it. Mr. Lee is a businessman,

587
00:32:06,650 --> 00:32:08,950
so he's generous like no other.

588
00:32:09,250 --> 00:32:10,320
In exchange,

589
00:32:10,850 --> 00:32:12,080
I have a condition.

590
00:32:12,350 --> 00:32:13,350
Sure.

591
00:32:14,250 --> 00:32:15,290
You.

592
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:18,720
Apologize to Jung Hee.

593
00:32:19,320 --> 00:32:21,690
Yes. We brought her here...

594
00:32:21,960 --> 00:32:25,000
to apologize and make up.

595
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:28,300
You. Get on your knees,
and beg for forgiveness.

596
00:32:33,610 --> 00:32:34,640
- What?
- What?

597
00:32:35,040 --> 00:32:36,310
What did he say?

598
00:32:36,940 --> 00:32:39,850
She was wrong, so she should beg.

599
00:32:40,450 --> 00:32:41,510
Are you insane?

600
00:32:41,750 --> 00:32:43,120
Watch your mouth.

601
00:32:43,650 --> 00:32:45,880
She almost drowned my precious daughter.

602
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:49,350
I should send her to jail
for the rest of her life.

603
00:32:50,390 --> 00:32:52,890
So... You.

604
00:32:53,790 --> 00:32:55,590
Get on your knees, and beg
Jung Hee for forgiveness.

605
00:32:58,930 --> 00:33:00,630
Do as he says.

606
00:33:01,900 --> 00:33:03,470
I can't do that.

607
00:33:05,600 --> 00:33:07,110
Jung Hee, come out.

608
00:33:07,370 --> 00:33:08,440
Jung Hee.

609
00:33:09,370 --> 00:33:11,510
Just expel me.

610
00:33:14,080 --> 00:33:16,220
The store your mom runs...

611
00:33:18,080 --> 00:33:20,990
My close friend owns the building.

612
00:33:21,550 --> 00:33:23,820
I can have him evict her, right?

613
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:26,120
Tomorrow.

614
00:33:26,790 --> 00:33:29,460
Father! That's not right.

615
00:33:31,160 --> 00:33:32,260
Is that okay?

616
00:33:33,570 --> 00:33:35,500
Please stop.

617
00:33:35,500 --> 00:33:37,940
I heard she's behind on rent anyway.

618
00:33:38,700 --> 00:33:40,840
She took out her deposit long ago.

619
00:33:41,640 --> 00:33:44,410
You know your mom has a bad rep, right?

620
00:33:45,940 --> 00:33:48,010
I wonder if he has a new tenant yet.

621
00:33:49,050 --> 00:33:50,820
Don't say that in front of a child.

622
00:33:50,950 --> 00:33:52,750
Ae Sook. What are you doing?

623
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:54,820
Sir.

624
00:33:55,250 --> 00:33:57,620
You can't do that to a child.

625
00:33:58,220 --> 00:34:00,260
The children were fighting...

626
00:34:04,260 --> 00:34:06,430
- I apologize.
- Hey, Ae Sook!

627
00:34:08,170 --> 00:34:09,940
Sorry, Jung Hee.

628
00:34:10,940 --> 00:34:13,810
I was wrong.

629
00:34:14,510 --> 00:34:17,110
Get up! Don't get on your knees.

630
00:34:17,340 --> 00:34:18,580
Get up!

631
00:34:19,950 --> 00:34:21,510
Father, how could you do this?

632
00:34:22,110 --> 00:34:24,180
You can't relieve your
guilt toward me like this.

633
00:34:25,250 --> 00:34:27,920
Get up! I said to get up! Get up!

634
00:34:39,160 --> 00:34:40,270
Jung Hee.

635
00:34:41,670 --> 00:34:43,740
Jung Hee.

636
00:34:44,100 --> 00:34:46,170
Don't be like that. Restrain yourself.

637
00:34:46,440 --> 00:34:48,670
Jung... Jung Hee.

638
00:34:50,710 --> 00:34:52,410
Jung Hee.

639
00:35:27,680 --> 00:35:29,310
I hated Ae Sook,

640
00:35:29,310 --> 00:35:30,950
who pushed me into the water,

641
00:35:31,780 --> 00:35:34,620
and I hated Hae Joo, who I felt...

642
00:35:34,890 --> 00:35:36,390
had won over Jin's heart,

643
00:35:37,460 --> 00:35:41,090
but the person I hated
the most was my father.

644
00:35:41,190 --> 00:35:43,000
- If you spend money...
- All he does...

645
00:35:43,000 --> 00:35:45,130
is raise his voice.

646
00:35:45,530 --> 00:35:47,430
What are you doing?

647
00:35:47,700 --> 00:35:50,640
He thinks the world revolves around him.

648
00:35:50,940 --> 00:35:52,870
- You should just die.
- Father.

649
00:35:52,870 --> 00:35:54,910
- Stop it!
- He never...

650
00:35:55,070 --> 00:35:56,880
admits his wrong.

651
00:35:57,580 --> 00:35:59,880
- He oppresses the weak...
- Get on your knees.

652
00:36:00,310 --> 00:36:03,280
In order to hide his embarrassing flaws.

653
00:36:06,420 --> 00:36:07,620
I...

654
00:36:08,490 --> 00:36:09,820
really hate...

655
00:36:10,690 --> 00:36:12,160
my father.

656
00:36:14,030 --> 00:36:16,160
- Hey.
- Hello, Mr. Lee.

657
00:36:16,860 --> 00:36:19,830
Did you come yourself to get cold medicine?

658
00:36:22,770 --> 00:36:23,800
Get to work.

659
00:36:25,470 --> 00:36:28,240
Hey. What do you need to put...

660
00:36:28,670 --> 00:36:29,840
on a burn?

661
00:36:30,340 --> 00:36:32,480
Did someone get burned? Who?

662
00:36:36,880 --> 00:36:38,950
- Give it to me.
- Yes, sir.

663
00:36:43,190 --> 00:36:44,220
Gosh.

664
00:37:39,680 --> 00:37:40,980
You scared me.

665
00:37:41,910 --> 00:37:42,920
What are you doing?

666
00:37:45,620 --> 00:37:46,720
Young Choon.

667
00:37:46,950 --> 00:37:50,660
Can you buy me some alcohol?

668
00:37:50,790 --> 00:37:53,330
You're too young to drink. It's late.

669
00:37:54,090 --> 00:37:56,630
Go home, and go to bed.

670
00:37:57,960 --> 00:38:00,300
Then I won't drink.

671
00:38:00,370 --> 00:38:03,340
Can't you just stay with me?

672
00:38:05,140 --> 00:38:06,510
Eng Cho is waiting.

673
00:38:12,680 --> 00:38:14,150
This is where you were.

674
00:38:15,780 --> 00:38:17,050
Want a drink?

675
00:38:21,890 --> 00:38:22,890
Ae Sook.

676
00:38:25,060 --> 00:38:26,390
Go home. Now.

677
00:38:29,230 --> 00:38:30,430
Fine, let's drink.

678
00:38:33,370 --> 00:38:35,100
Let's drink until we die.

679
00:38:36,200 --> 00:38:37,300
Hey, Peanut.

680
00:38:38,100 --> 00:38:39,540
I said to go home.

681
00:38:41,270 --> 00:38:43,410
Thanks, Young Choon,

682
00:38:44,010 --> 00:38:45,240
for lending me your girlfriend.

683
00:38:55,320 --> 00:38:56,460
Let's go.

684
00:39:01,690 --> 00:39:03,560
It was about 1:20am.

685
00:39:04,030 --> 00:39:06,800
I went out to go to the bathroom,

686
00:39:06,800 --> 00:39:08,700
- and...
- Bam!

687
00:39:08,830 --> 00:39:12,370
The tenant girl brought
her boyfriend again?

688
00:39:13,910 --> 00:39:15,440
What were they doing?

689
00:39:15,610 --> 00:39:18,410
They were shuffling around
for a while, and then...

690
00:39:18,740 --> 00:39:20,910
I heard some strange ripping sound.

691
00:39:21,250 --> 00:39:22,380
Ripping sound?

692
00:39:22,480 --> 00:39:24,050
Did they break something?

693
00:39:24,180 --> 00:39:25,780
No.

694
00:39:26,790 --> 00:39:29,490
It was the sound of her blouse ripping.

695
00:39:29,660 --> 00:39:31,960
Her blouse ripped.

696
00:39:32,520 --> 00:39:33,560
Then...

697
00:39:33,860 --> 00:39:35,930
Hae Joo came to me,

698
00:39:36,560 --> 00:39:40,100
but I couldn't get myself to go to her.

699
00:39:40,100 --> 00:39:42,130
"Look." That's what he said.

700
00:39:42,330 --> 00:39:44,540
I wanted to believe her,

701
00:39:45,300 --> 00:39:48,640
but I couldn't stop
thinking that there was...

702
00:39:48,810 --> 00:39:50,340
something going on with her and Jin.

703
00:39:51,410 --> 00:39:52,440
Why is that?

704
00:39:53,580 --> 00:39:56,110
What is it? I didn't hear the bell.

705
00:39:56,680 --> 00:39:59,520
We don't have math this period.

706
00:39:59,520 --> 00:40:00,850
Okay, okay. Quiet.

707
00:40:01,150 --> 00:40:03,820
I rushed over...

708
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:06,490
to share the news...

709
00:40:06,630 --> 00:40:08,960
of a very happy event in our class...

710
00:40:08,960 --> 00:40:11,500
as soon as possible.

711
00:40:12,100 --> 00:40:14,630
Park Hae Joo of our class...

712
00:40:15,270 --> 00:40:18,900
scored the highest in the nation...

713
00:40:19,370 --> 00:40:22,110
on the national mock exam this semester.

714
00:40:22,310 --> 00:40:23,640
Amazing.

715
00:40:25,940 --> 00:40:27,050
Mr. Oh!

716
00:40:28,780 --> 00:40:31,920
We took that mock exam...

717
00:40:33,190 --> 00:40:35,150
- before she came.
- What?

718
00:40:35,150 --> 00:40:37,120
What are you talking about?

719
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:39,960
She scored the highest in the nation.

720
00:40:40,160 --> 00:40:43,260
It doesn't matter where she took the exam.

721
00:40:43,260 --> 00:40:45,700
It's all the same, idiot.

722
00:40:45,830 --> 00:40:47,730
Also, I just heard...

723
00:40:47,770 --> 00:40:51,240
that Hae Joo came in
first in the National...

724
00:40:52,370 --> 00:40:55,610
Presidential Essay Competition,

725
00:40:55,610 --> 00:40:57,210
Poetry Component.

726
00:40:59,610 --> 00:41:02,780
Okay. Hae Joo. Please stand up.

727
00:41:03,820 --> 00:41:05,350
Go on.

728
00:41:09,120 --> 00:41:11,460
Our class' treasure. Our diamond.

729
00:41:11,720 --> 00:41:13,430
Let's give Hae Joo...

730
00:41:13,690 --> 00:41:15,960
a warm round of applause!

731
00:41:25,740 --> 00:41:26,910
That's right.

732
00:41:27,770 --> 00:41:30,180
I don't compare to Hae Joo.

733
00:41:30,510 --> 00:41:32,740
We will now begin the
afternoon broadcast...

734
00:41:32,950 --> 00:41:34,850
by Jeonghyeon's broadcasting club.

735
00:41:41,420 --> 00:41:42,990
In every aspect.

736
00:41:44,560 --> 00:41:46,490
Hae Joo!

737
00:41:47,190 --> 00:41:49,930
Where are you? Hae Joo!

738
00:41:49,960 --> 00:41:51,700
- Hae Joo!
- She's coming.

739
00:41:51,700 --> 00:41:54,400
- She's so pretty.
- Quiet.

740
00:41:54,500 --> 00:41:56,000
Have you eaten?

741
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:57,870
The thought...

742
00:41:58,540 --> 00:42:01,870
that I don't come close to Hae Joo...

743
00:42:01,970 --> 00:42:05,140
as being Jin's girlfriend won't stop...

744
00:42:06,180 --> 00:42:08,010
tormenting me.

745
00:42:08,110 --> 00:42:10,250
Those guys are so pathetic.

746
00:42:11,320 --> 00:42:13,420
Jung Hee. Your brother is the worst...

747
00:42:13,420 --> 00:42:15,020
among them.

748
00:42:15,220 --> 00:42:16,790
Then what am I...

749
00:42:17,590 --> 00:42:18,890
supposed to do?

750
00:42:18,960 --> 00:42:20,960
Get lost! Scram!

751
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:22,260
What do you mean?

752
00:42:22,430 --> 00:42:24,260
Tell your brother...

753
00:42:24,530 --> 00:42:26,060
to get it together.

754
00:42:26,060 --> 00:42:27,770
What else can I do?

755
00:42:27,930 --> 00:42:30,100
I'll have to expose the truth.

756
00:42:30,100 --> 00:42:31,970
What? Expose what?

757
00:42:32,340 --> 00:42:33,540
You guys go ahead.

758
00:42:33,610 --> 00:42:34,670
Jung Hee!

759
00:42:34,670 --> 00:42:36,880
Look. It's Jin.

760
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:43,050
(Gyeryoon High School)

761
00:42:43,050 --> 00:42:45,050
- Jin.
- Jin.

762
00:42:52,930 --> 00:42:54,160
Who's she?

763
00:42:54,260 --> 00:42:55,330
Jung Hee.

764
00:42:56,200 --> 00:42:57,460
Are you okay now?

765
00:43:09,010 --> 00:43:10,080
What is it?

766
00:43:10,410 --> 00:43:11,580
Jin.

767
00:43:12,640 --> 00:43:15,680
What's going on with you and Hae Joo?

768
00:43:17,080 --> 00:43:18,220
Hae Joo says...

769
00:43:18,480 --> 00:43:20,850
there's nothing between you, but...

770
00:43:24,790 --> 00:43:27,990
But I wanted to confirm with you.

771
00:43:28,460 --> 00:43:31,660
Do you like Hae Joo?

772
00:43:32,760 --> 00:43:34,730
Please tell me the truth.

773
00:43:36,470 --> 00:43:39,000
If you do,

774
00:43:40,840 --> 00:43:43,140
I'm going to stop...

775
00:43:46,510 --> 00:43:47,950
liking you.

776
00:43:52,050 --> 00:43:53,050
Jung Hee.

777
00:43:54,150 --> 00:43:56,460
You're spunkier than I thought.

778
00:43:57,420 --> 00:43:59,930
Please tell me.

779
00:44:02,060 --> 00:44:03,100
Hae Joo...

780
00:44:05,700 --> 00:44:06,730
Hae Joo...

781
00:44:10,340 --> 00:44:12,400
She's just a good friend.

782
00:44:17,810 --> 00:44:18,910
Is that true?

783
00:44:21,010 --> 00:44:22,180
Dong Moon.

784
00:44:25,680 --> 00:44:26,850
Hello.

785
00:44:27,190 --> 00:44:28,490
I'm sorry for interrupting.

786
00:44:28,590 --> 00:44:31,890
I'm Baek Dong Moon. I'm a junior.

787
00:44:31,960 --> 00:44:34,760
We met at the meeting of representatives.

788
00:44:35,290 --> 00:44:36,300
Really?

789
00:44:36,300 --> 00:44:38,660
What are you doing? Leave.

790
00:44:40,070 --> 00:44:41,130
Jung Hee...

791
00:44:42,970 --> 00:44:45,770
was in a lot of pain because of you.

792
00:44:46,940 --> 00:44:48,540
That's why I'm being rude...

793
00:44:48,840 --> 00:44:50,980
and asking you again to be sure.

794
00:44:53,580 --> 00:44:54,580
Do you...

795
00:44:55,680 --> 00:44:56,680
like Jung Hee?

796
00:44:56,680 --> 00:44:59,320
- No.
- Yes, I like her.

797
00:44:59,380 --> 00:45:00,390
Hey!

798
00:45:02,350 --> 00:45:05,460
You're in the heart of the girl I like,

799
00:45:06,190 --> 00:45:08,130
so I'm not all that happy.

800
00:45:08,490 --> 00:45:09,500
However,

801
00:45:10,960 --> 00:45:12,600
I'm afraid she'll get hurt...

802
00:45:12,600 --> 00:45:13,700
Dong Moon.

803
00:45:14,970 --> 00:45:16,170
Stop it.

804
00:45:16,770 --> 00:45:17,770
Dong Moon.

805
00:45:18,640 --> 00:45:19,640
You're cute.

806
00:45:20,310 --> 00:45:22,310
But you know your doing this...

807
00:45:23,010 --> 00:45:25,210
to a senior is very out of line,

808
00:45:26,810 --> 00:45:27,880
don't you?

809
00:45:28,580 --> 00:45:30,780
Yes, I do know.

810
00:45:31,820 --> 00:45:32,920
I'm sorry.

811
00:45:36,220 --> 00:45:38,020
Fine. As long as you know.

812
00:45:39,830 --> 00:45:40,830
Jung Hee.

813
00:45:41,590 --> 00:45:42,630
Goodbye.

814
00:45:47,570 --> 00:45:48,730
Wait!

815
00:45:57,040 --> 00:45:59,580
Young Choon. I'm here
to pick up my medicine.

816
00:45:59,580 --> 00:46:00,950
Just a minute.

817
00:46:01,580 --> 00:46:03,120
First in the nation?

818
00:46:03,550 --> 00:46:05,320
Not first in Daegu?

819
00:46:05,320 --> 00:46:07,320
No. First in the nation.

820
00:46:07,320 --> 00:46:10,520
My gosh. Someone like
that moved into our town?

821
00:46:10,520 --> 00:46:12,890
Yes. Hae Joo's father...

822
00:46:12,890 --> 00:46:15,060
is a professor at Seoul University.

823
00:46:15,060 --> 00:46:17,460
Oh my gosh. Why did someone like that...

824
00:46:17,460 --> 00:46:19,200
move down here?

825
00:46:19,630 --> 00:46:20,770
I don't know.

826
00:46:24,070 --> 00:46:25,540
- Here you go.
- How much is it?

827
00:46:25,900 --> 00:46:26,940
That will be 50 cents.

828
00:46:28,040 --> 00:46:29,040
Here.

829
00:46:30,580 --> 00:46:31,840
Have a nice day.

830
00:46:32,040 --> 00:46:33,050
You too.

831
00:46:58,970 --> 00:47:00,310
Who do you think you are?

832
00:47:00,640 --> 00:47:02,540
How could you follow me there?

833
00:47:02,640 --> 00:47:03,640
Me?

834
00:47:06,910 --> 00:47:08,550
The man who likes Jung Hee.

835
00:47:09,650 --> 00:47:11,820
- I told you.
- Dong Moon.

836
00:47:12,280 --> 00:47:13,890
I'm warning you.

837
00:47:13,890 --> 00:47:15,190
Don't do that again.

838
00:47:15,190 --> 00:47:17,120
You're free to like me,

839
00:47:17,120 --> 00:47:18,320
but I won't condone...

840
00:47:18,320 --> 00:47:20,090
your meddling like this, got it?

841
00:47:21,730 --> 00:47:23,100
Don't you do this either.

842
00:47:24,030 --> 00:47:25,700
Even if you like Jin,

843
00:47:25,700 --> 00:47:27,530
you shouldn't show up at the school.

844
00:47:31,670 --> 00:47:32,770
That's up to me.

845
00:47:34,610 --> 00:47:35,840
It's up to me too.

846
00:47:42,410 --> 00:47:43,420
Are you hungry?

847
00:47:45,220 --> 00:47:47,490
- Want some pastries?
- Eat by yourself!

848
00:47:47,650 --> 00:47:49,090
You always want to eat pastries.

849
00:48:05,900 --> 00:48:07,040
Hello.

850
00:48:09,980 --> 00:48:11,140
Wait a few minutes.

851
00:48:11,310 --> 00:48:12,850
The pharmacist will be back soon.

852
00:48:13,280 --> 00:48:14,350
Well...

853
00:48:15,410 --> 00:48:17,880
I need a bandage...

854
00:48:18,180 --> 00:48:20,850
for a cut on the hand...

855
00:48:21,390 --> 00:48:22,590
How?

856
00:48:33,330 --> 00:48:34,770
Not me.

857
00:48:41,170 --> 00:48:42,880
A guest...

858
00:48:43,080 --> 00:48:45,380
cut his hand and I think...

859
00:48:46,750 --> 00:48:48,650
it got infected.

860
00:48:50,050 --> 00:48:52,220
Well, if that's the case,

861
00:48:52,890 --> 00:48:54,290
he should go to the hospital.

862
00:48:57,620 --> 00:49:00,460
He can't go to the hospital.

863
00:49:11,370 --> 00:49:13,810
I said to stop following me.

864
00:49:15,610 --> 00:49:17,240
I wasn't following you.

865
00:49:18,080 --> 00:49:20,610
I'm going to visit my friend,

866
00:49:21,280 --> 00:49:22,580
Bong Soo.

867
00:49:26,420 --> 00:49:27,420
Okay then.

868
00:49:29,790 --> 00:49:31,560
Come home safely.

869
00:49:44,070 --> 00:49:46,910
The infection looks bad.

870
00:49:46,910 --> 00:49:48,140
You need a doctor,

871
00:49:48,140 --> 00:49:50,080
but you're on the run... Hae Joo.

872
00:49:53,880 --> 00:49:55,380
It must hurt a lot.

873
00:49:57,050 --> 00:49:58,480
Okay. All done.

874
00:50:06,190 --> 00:50:07,430
Eng Cho.

875
00:50:10,360 --> 00:50:12,970
My goodness. When did you come?

876
00:50:13,200 --> 00:50:15,500
It's okay. Don't cry.

877
00:50:15,500 --> 00:50:18,800
It's okay. Don't cry. That's a good girl.

878
00:50:33,150 --> 00:50:34,150
Hae Joo...

879
00:50:35,390 --> 00:50:37,590
She's just a good friend.

880
00:51:01,750 --> 00:51:03,280
Hey.

881
00:51:03,280 --> 00:51:06,190
You saved Jung Hee's life.

882
00:51:06,190 --> 00:51:08,520
This is all I can do to thank you.

883
00:51:08,520 --> 00:51:10,260
Eat up. Eat.

884
00:51:10,560 --> 00:51:13,790
You're not a picky eater, are you?

885
00:51:13,990 --> 00:51:17,030
Bong Soo, this brat, is so finicky.

886
00:51:17,030 --> 00:51:18,700
That's why he's so skinny.

887
00:51:19,000 --> 00:51:21,670
No. I'm not picky at all.

888
00:51:21,970 --> 00:51:22,970
Thank you.

889
00:51:22,970 --> 00:51:25,140
You look like you wouldn't be picky.

890
00:51:25,340 --> 00:51:26,340
Eat up.

891
00:51:27,510 --> 00:51:29,110
Why are you hitting him?

892
00:51:29,540 --> 00:51:30,540
Eat up.

893
00:51:30,640 --> 00:51:32,240
- What a liar.
- Goodness.

894
00:51:32,240 --> 00:51:34,380
You're such a good eater.

895
00:51:34,510 --> 00:51:36,720
Here. Eat this.

896
00:51:36,720 --> 00:51:38,450
You should eat it whole,

897
00:51:38,450 --> 00:51:40,120
including the bone.

898
00:51:40,120 --> 00:51:41,220
Try it.

899
00:51:41,620 --> 00:51:43,890
That's it. Eat it all up.

900
00:51:44,360 --> 00:51:47,930
Goodness. Try some of this too.

901
00:51:47,930 --> 00:51:49,630
Here. Try this.

902
00:51:49,630 --> 00:51:50,630
Gosh.

903
00:51:51,130 --> 00:51:53,000
What a good eater.

904
00:51:53,000 --> 00:51:54,100
Eng Cho.

905
00:51:55,000 --> 00:51:56,200
Eng Cho.

906
00:51:58,600 --> 00:51:59,610
Eng Cho.

907
00:52:03,410 --> 00:52:04,410
Eng Cho.

908
00:52:10,280 --> 00:52:11,420
Eng Cho!

909
00:52:12,480 --> 00:52:13,490
Your turn.

910
00:52:14,150 --> 00:52:15,220
Eng Cho!

911
00:52:18,920 --> 00:52:20,960
Have you seen Eng Cho?

912
00:52:20,990 --> 00:52:22,660
- I didn't.
- No?

913
00:52:22,730 --> 00:52:23,760
No.

914
00:52:24,660 --> 00:52:26,400
- You didn't?
- No, I didn't.

915
00:52:34,640 --> 00:52:36,040
A gangster doesn't become a saint...

916
00:52:36,040 --> 00:52:37,240
by living like this.

917
00:52:38,440 --> 00:52:39,480
Eng Cho!

918
00:52:41,210 --> 00:52:42,450
Young Choon.

919
00:52:45,080 --> 00:52:47,790
- Where did you go?
- I was with Hae Joo.

920
00:52:48,420 --> 00:52:50,620
She braided my hair...

921
00:52:50,690 --> 00:52:52,290
pretty like this,

922
00:52:52,290 --> 00:52:54,260
- and made me donuts...
- You brat.

923
00:52:54,260 --> 00:52:56,260
You brat. You little brat.

924
00:52:56,830 --> 00:52:58,300
I told you not to go there.

925
00:52:58,300 --> 00:53:00,300
You scared me. I thought you went missing.

926
00:53:00,300 --> 00:53:02,840
- Why won't you listen?
- Stop.

927
00:53:04,440 --> 00:53:07,840
I'm sorry. I assumed she had told you.

928
00:53:09,270 --> 00:53:11,410
Do you think Eng Cho is a beggar?

929
00:53:12,110 --> 00:53:14,010
Did I ask you to do that?

930
00:53:19,950 --> 00:53:21,020
Let's go.

931
00:53:28,290 --> 00:53:30,160
It's dark already.

932
00:53:30,260 --> 00:53:31,930
Get home quickly.

933
00:53:32,400 --> 00:53:34,700
Yes, ma'am. The food was delicious.

934
00:53:34,700 --> 00:53:35,730
Thanks.

935
00:53:35,730 --> 00:53:37,700
- See you tomorrow.
- Okay.

936
00:53:37,700 --> 00:53:40,110
- Bye. Don't come back.
- Shut it.

937
00:53:40,640 --> 00:53:41,670
Goodbye.

938
00:53:44,980 --> 00:53:46,510
What? Why aren't you going?

939
00:53:46,780 --> 00:53:47,980
Do you need to poop?

940
00:53:49,110 --> 00:53:51,250
No, that's not it.

941
00:53:53,020 --> 00:53:54,350
You're still here?

942
00:53:55,350 --> 00:53:56,720
- Jung Hee.
- Bye.

943
00:53:57,120 --> 00:53:59,490
Look how that brat talks.

944
00:54:00,260 --> 00:54:02,790
- Bye.
- Okay. Good night.

945
00:54:05,800 --> 00:54:07,770
Be careful of gangsters!

946
00:54:07,900 --> 00:54:08,930
Okay.

947
00:54:10,370 --> 00:54:12,840
He has a great voice too.

948
00:54:13,470 --> 00:54:16,040
How is he so mature?

949
00:54:17,110 --> 00:54:18,740
Just make him your son-in-law.

950
00:54:18,910 --> 00:54:20,850
You don't think I will?

951
00:54:28,120 --> 00:54:29,620
Maybe I overate.

952
00:54:30,490 --> 00:54:32,620
I need a bathroom.

953
00:55:02,820 --> 00:55:04,560
Will you tell me the truth?

954
00:55:04,690 --> 00:55:07,360
What's going on between you and Jin?

955
00:55:07,360 --> 00:55:08,760
There's nothing going on between us.

956
00:55:11,560 --> 00:55:12,630
Yes.

957
00:55:13,530 --> 00:55:14,630
Let's make up.

958
00:55:26,780 --> 00:55:28,050
Jin?

959
00:55:35,390 --> 00:55:37,190
Whom is he waiting for?

960
00:55:45,800 --> 00:55:47,800
- Why are you back?
- You said...

961
00:55:48,970 --> 00:55:50,800
you have no feelings for me...

962
00:55:51,640 --> 00:55:52,800
to Jung Hee?

963
00:55:54,740 --> 00:55:55,740
Yes.

964
00:55:56,340 --> 00:55:58,580
I thought I should be honest with her.

965
00:56:00,210 --> 00:56:01,250
Hae Joo.

966
00:56:01,980 --> 00:56:03,620
Why don't you understand how I feel?

967
00:56:05,250 --> 00:56:06,720
I really like you.

968
00:56:07,020 --> 00:56:09,720
I can't study because of you. My grades...

969
00:56:09,960 --> 00:56:11,160
keep falling. I'm going crazy.

970
00:56:12,090 --> 00:56:13,830
What must I do for you to like me?

971
00:56:14,660 --> 00:56:15,860
I'm sorry.

972
00:56:16,130 --> 00:56:19,460
You can't control how a person feels.

973
00:56:21,670 --> 00:56:23,200
I need to go back in.

974
00:56:24,170 --> 00:56:25,200
Good night.

975
00:56:26,570 --> 00:56:27,640
Hae Joo.

976
00:56:29,210 --> 00:56:30,310
Then...

977
00:56:31,110 --> 00:56:33,410
did he lie to me?

978
00:56:34,710 --> 00:56:35,950
How?

979
00:56:36,750 --> 00:56:37,980
How?

980
00:56:38,520 --> 00:56:39,720
Jin.

981
00:56:45,020 --> 00:56:46,090
What is it?

982
00:56:48,030 --> 00:56:49,430
Were you listening in?

983
00:56:49,430 --> 00:56:51,130
It wasn't intentional.

984
00:56:51,660 --> 00:56:54,700
Jin. Why did you lie to Jung Hee?

985
00:56:55,000 --> 00:56:56,130
What?

986
00:57:00,910 --> 00:57:02,210
I have nothing to say to you.

987
00:57:06,610 --> 00:57:09,150
You need to be clear
about things like this.

988
00:57:09,250 --> 00:57:11,850
Not telling the truth to
avoid hurting someone...

989
00:57:12,120 --> 00:57:14,290
- isn't for the person...
- Dong Moon.

990
00:57:18,390 --> 00:57:20,760
- Leave.
- I can't go like this.

991
00:57:22,290 --> 00:57:23,700
Tell Jung Hee the truth.

992
00:57:23,700 --> 00:57:25,830
Step aside. Do you want a beating?

993
00:57:25,960 --> 00:57:27,100
Want to try me?

994
00:57:28,330 --> 00:57:29,400
Shall I?

995
00:57:32,470 --> 00:57:35,770
If we fight and I beat you,

996
00:57:36,340 --> 00:57:38,280
please tell Jung Hee the truth.

997
00:57:38,280 --> 00:57:39,710
You little punk.

998
00:57:46,120 --> 00:57:48,650
Are you okay? Watch it next time.

999
00:57:50,090 --> 00:57:51,590
I'm not done yet.

1000
00:58:09,370 --> 00:58:10,440
Dong Moon.

1001
00:58:11,140 --> 00:58:12,610
Don't just study.

1002
00:58:13,380 --> 00:58:15,310
Exercise a little too.

1003
00:58:21,190 --> 00:58:22,320
See you at school.

1004
00:58:35,430 --> 00:58:36,600
That's what it was.

1005
00:58:36,600 --> 00:58:37,700
Jin!

1006
00:58:38,070 --> 00:58:39,200
I saw only...

1007
00:58:39,270 --> 00:58:41,470
- what I wanted to.
- Hey.

1008
00:58:42,310 --> 00:58:43,540
I had no idea.

1009
00:58:44,810 --> 00:58:47,250
She must be in a lot of pain. Oh, no.

1010
00:58:49,450 --> 00:58:50,820
I had no idea...

1011
00:58:51,520 --> 00:58:54,050
that Jin liked Hae Joo from the start.

1012
00:59:39,770 --> 00:59:40,830
Jung Hee.

1013
00:59:40,970 --> 00:59:42,600
Who hit you?

1014
00:59:45,770 --> 00:59:48,840
I met a gangster over there earlier.

1015
00:59:49,540 --> 00:59:51,440
I would've fought back if
there were one or two,

1016
00:59:52,610 --> 00:59:54,780
but eight of them jumped me at once.

1017
01:00:04,360 --> 01:00:05,460
Wipe your mouth.

1018
01:00:06,530 --> 01:00:09,390
I can't use that. It's too precious.

1019
01:00:12,260 --> 01:00:13,770
Wipe it already.

1020
01:00:16,270 --> 01:00:17,600
That hurts.

1021
01:00:21,170 --> 01:00:22,340
Are you crying?

1022
01:00:25,440 --> 01:00:28,410
Why? Because I got hurt?

1023
01:00:29,620 --> 01:00:30,950
Don't be stupid.

1024
01:00:35,820 --> 01:00:37,960
Then why?

1025
01:00:46,270 --> 01:00:47,970
I got in trouble with my dad.

1026
01:00:51,040 --> 01:00:52,100
You did?

1027
01:00:55,970 --> 01:00:57,240
Then cry.

1028
01:01:00,050 --> 01:01:01,650
You'll feel better.

1029
01:01:03,150 --> 01:01:04,320
Should I?

1030
01:01:06,020 --> 01:01:07,490
Should I cry a little?

1031
01:01:10,360 --> 01:01:11,460
Cry.

1032
01:01:13,490 --> 01:01:14,860
I'll stand guard.

1033
01:01:42,150 --> 01:01:43,660
Why are you crying?

1034
01:01:45,190 --> 01:01:46,230
I...

1035
01:01:47,630 --> 01:01:48,690
I...

1036
01:01:50,760 --> 01:01:52,760
Because the wounds hurt.

1037
01:01:54,530 --> 01:01:57,640
I'm crying because I'm so upset...

1038
01:01:58,770 --> 01:02:00,840
because I can't win your love.

1039
01:02:02,170 --> 01:02:05,510
Because I don't compare at all to Jin.

1040
01:02:07,110 --> 01:02:08,450
You should cry too.

1041
01:02:09,180 --> 01:02:10,980
You'll feel better.

1042
01:03:12,880 --> 01:03:15,450
(Girls' Generation 1979)

1043
01:03:16,680 --> 01:03:18,920
Be proud and confident.

1044
01:03:18,920 --> 01:03:20,790
I'm over Jin now.

1045
01:03:20,790 --> 01:03:21,920
You mean it?

1046
01:03:22,250 --> 01:03:23,520
It's not over.

1047
01:03:23,520 --> 01:03:25,760
I won't forget your dad
making me get on my knees.

1048
01:03:25,760 --> 01:03:28,660
- An after party?
- Jin is coming too.

1049
01:03:29,190 --> 01:03:32,030
Did you know that Jin
keeps hitting on Hae Joo?

1050
01:03:32,930 --> 01:03:35,170
- Please help me.
- Sorry?

1051
01:03:35,370 --> 01:03:36,370
A study room?

1052
01:03:36,370 --> 01:03:37,370
I'll give you my pass.

1053
01:03:37,370 --> 01:03:39,610
Does that mean I'll be spending...

1054
01:03:39,610 --> 01:03:41,810
my first night with Jin tonight?
